channel.title: PF Config
channel.description:
I just downloaded the Port Forwarding Config It brought up a page with a list of Router Manufactors and Models.
I look at my Router, and I found the manufactor (Scientific Atlanta) but it isn't on the select list that the PFConfig brings up.
Have I found the wrong name? I looked all around my router, and it looks like thats the manufactor.
So, what do I do if I cant find the name on the PF Config window of my router?
